genresAdvancedInfo.name: detske pisnicky
genresAdvancedInfo.description: "detske pisnicky" - This is a genre of music that is specifically targeted towards children. The songs are usually upbeat and catchy, with lyrics that are easy for kids to sing along to. The themes of the songs are often related to childhood experiences such as friendship, playtime, and family.
